title: At least 4 countries pull out of 2026 Eurovision contest over Israel's participation
description: Ireland, the Netherlands, Spain and Slovenia said they were pulling out of the contest after organizers decided to allow Israel to continue to compete, despite tensions over its conduct in Gaza.
